# Build markers written by scripts/make-release.sh and the deploy
# helpers. Not versioned to avoid merge conflicts on every release —
# Util\Build::init() reads them from the project root at runtime.
/BUILD
/.version

# Release artefacts produced by scripts/make-release.sh and uploaded
# to the GitHub release page as assets. Not versioned (re-built per
# release).
/tylio-admin-bundle-*.tar.gz
/tylio-source-*.tar.gz

# Legacy: an older Vite config wrote the admin SPA here. Ignored so
# leftover copies on existing checkouts don't pollute commits.
# We ignore the CONTENTS (not the directory itself) so the exception
# below can re-include the compat sentinel — git's negation rule
# requires the parent dir not to be fully ignored.
/public/*
# Exception: keep the compat sentinel for the v0.3.1 UpdateApplier
# (see public/index.php for the full rationale).
!/public/index.php
